    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. While the engine does start, it suffers from a severe head gasket leak and a failing alternator, meaning it is not currently roadworthy for anything beyond a short trip to a shop. The body shows significant rust along the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and in need of replacement. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no warranties, and will likely require more in repairs than its current market value to return to reliable operation.",
      "price": 3200.0,
